{
  "video_id": "lMPiz7clTyc",
  "language": "en",
  "entries": [
    {
      "text": "People think living in Korea means",
      "start": 1.28,
      "duration": 3.12
    },
    {
      "text": "you're always surrounded by friends.",
      "start": 2.879,
      "duration": 2.801
    },
    {
      "text": "While that might be true for some",
      "start": 4.4,
      "duration": 3.2
    },
    {
      "text": "people, it's not so for me, and that's",
      "start": 5.68,
      "duration": 3.76
    },
    {
      "text": "by choice. This is what it's like to",
      "start": 7.6,
      "duration": 5.56
    },
    {
      "text": "live alone in Soul.",
      "start": 9.44,
      "duration": 3.72
    },
    {
      "text": "Since it's 11:00 a.m. on a weekday, the",
      "start": 21.119,
      "duration": 6.201
    },
    {
      "text": "subway is relatively quiet.",
      "start": 23.119,
      "duration": 4.201
    },
    {
      "text": "Korean winters somewhat feel colder than",
      "start": 45.52,
      "duration": 4.719
    },
    {
      "text": "anywhere else. After quickly",
      "start": 47.84,
      "duration": 7.08
    },
    {
      "text": "transferring to a bus, I head back home.",
      "start": 50.239,
      "duration": 4.681
    },
    {
      "text": "I usually go out to film in the morning.",
      "start": 60.879,
      "duration": 6.761
    },
    {
      "text": "That way, the day feels a little longer.",
      "start": 63.039,
      "duration": 4.601
    },
    {
      "text": "When I get back home, the very first",
      "start": 71.92,
      "duration": 6.36
    },
    {
      "text": "thing I do is enjoy a cup of coffee.",
      "start": 73.68,
      "duration": 4.6
    },
    {
      "text": "I love hazing americanos and lately I've",
      "start": 88.0,
      "duration": 4.159
    },
    {
      "text": "been obsessed with a Japanese capsule",
      "start": 90.64,
      "duration": 3.519
    },
    {
      "text": "coffee which I ordered off of Kuban",
      "start": 92.159,
      "duration": 3.28
    },
    {
      "text": "which is one of the biggest delivery",
      "start": 94.159,
      "duration": 5.241
    },
    {
      "text": "apps here in South Korea.",
      "start": 95.439,
      "duration": 3.961
    },
    {
      "text": "My life doesn't seem exciting from the",
      "start": 106.799,
      "duration": 4.0
    },
    {
      "text": "outside. No big plans, no constant",
      "start": 108.72,
      "duration": 3.759
    },
    {
      "text": "noise. I like it that way. Some people",
      "start": 110.799,
      "duration": 6.121
    },
    {
      "text": "might call it boring, but I like boring.",
      "start": 112.479,
      "duration": 4.441
    },
    {
      "text": "As expected, watching TV at this hour is",
      "start": 142.4,
      "duration": 5.88
    },
    {
      "text": "very boring.",
      "start": 144.959,
      "duration": 3.321
    },
    {
      "text": "It's about time to start doing some",
      "start": 164.16,
      "duration": 4.84
    },
    {
      "text": "house chores.",
      "start": 165.76,
      "duration": 3.24
    },
    {
      "text": "I'm the type of person who cleans as I",
      "start": 175.599,
      "duration": 3.761
    },
    {
      "text": "go instead of putting things off. That",
      "start": 177.36,
      "duration": 4.4
    },
    {
      "text": "way, less dust builds up and cleaning",
      "start": 179.36,
      "duration": 4.799
    },
    {
      "text": "feels a lot easier. How about you? Do",
      "start": 181.76,
      "duration": 3.92
    },
    {
      "text": "you clean every day like me or do you",
      "start": 184.159,
      "duration": 3.121
    },
    {
      "text": "save it all for one deep cleaning",
      "start": 185.68,
      "duration": 4.6
    },
    {
      "text": "section?",
      "start": 187.28,
      "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
      "text": "The longer I live in Korea, the more",
      "start": 205.28,
      "duration": 3.76
    },
    {
      "text": "furniture I seem to accumulate, which",
      "start": 207.2,
      "duration": 6.679
    },
    {
      "text": "means there's even more to clean.",
      "start": 209.04,
      "duration": 4.839
    },
    {
      "text": "I graduated from a university in Korea",
      "start": 223.84,
      "duration": 4.16
    },
    {
      "text": "outside the city and moved to Soul 6",
      "start": 225.92,
      "duration": 3.92
    },
    {
      "text": "years ago. And here everyone is busy",
      "start": 228.0,
      "duration": 4.84
    },
    {
      "text": "surviving.",
      "start": 229.84,
      "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
      "text": "Work doesn't end at 5 and energy is a",
      "start": 255.04,
      "duration": 4.319
    },
    {
      "text": "limited resource. So after a full day,",
      "start": 257.12,
      "duration": 4.239
    },
    {
      "text": "socializing starts to feel like another",
      "start": 259.359,
      "duration": 5.0
    },
    {
      "text": "obligation.",
      "start": 261.359,
      "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
      "text": "It's not that I don't like people. I",
      "start": 280.639,
      "duration": 3.521
    },
    {
      "text": "just don't enjoy forced conversation,",
      "start": 282.4,
      "duration": 3.6
    },
    {
      "text": "surface level friendship, or showing up",
      "start": 284.16,
      "duration": 5.72
    },
    {
      "text": "just to say I showed up.",
      "start": 286.0,
      "duration": 3.88
    },
    {
      "text": "As someone that is introverted, I don't",
      "start": 298.72,
      "duration": 3.6
    },
    {
      "text": "go to group dinners and I also don't",
      "start": 300.479,
      "duration": 4.841
    },
    {
      "text": "drink.",
      "start": 302.32,
      "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
      "text": "I train my beds once a week.",
      "start": 326.0,
      "duration": 4.759
    },
    {
      "text": "In Korea, socializing often comes in",
      "start": 344.479,
      "duration": 3.841
    },
    {
      "text": "specific formats. Group dinners,",
      "start": 346.56,
      "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
      "text": "drinking culture, hierarchy, and",
      "start": 348.32,
      "duration": 4.68
    },
    {
      "text": "espions.",
      "start": 350.0,
      "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
      "text": "I usually ventilate the room while",
      "start": 376.96,
      "duration": 4.16
    },
    {
      "text": "vacuuming, but today it's just too cold,",
      "start": 378.56,
      "duration": 6.28
    },
    {
      "text": "so I skipped it.",
      "start": 381.12,
      "duration": 3.72
    },
    {
      "text": "Heat. Heat.",
      "start": 386.88,
      "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
      "text": "Even in a oneperson household, dishes",
      "start": 426.639,
      "duration": 6.28
    },
    {
      "text": "pile up, so it's unavoidable.",
      "start": 428.72,
      "duration": 4.199
    },
    {
      "text": "Since the sink is low, this position is",
      "start": 433.28,
      "duration": 5.6
    },
    {
      "text": "the most comfortable for me.",
      "start": 435.28,
      "duration": 3.6
    },
    {
      "text": "It's time for my second break of the",
      "start": 444.4,
      "duration": 3.68
    },
    {
      "text": "day.",
      "start": 446.16,
      "duration": 3.759
    },
    {
      "text": "While watching TV, I scroll through",
      "start": 448.08,
      "duration": 6.519
    },
    {
      "text": "Coupang Eats to decide what to eat.",
      "start": 449.919,
      "duration": 4.68
    },
    {
      "text": "Living in Korea, Kopang has become",
      "start": 472.4,
      "duration": 5.799
    },
    {
      "text": "basically a necessity.",
      "start": 474.479,
      "duration": 3.72
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Typically, food delivery times in toll",
      "start": 483.44,
      "duration": 4.0
    },
    {
      "text": "takes about 30 to 40 minutes to be",
      "start": 485.44,
      "duration": 3.759
    },
    {
      "text": "delivered to your doorstep and in some",
      "start": 487.44,
      "duration": 4.0
    },
    {
      "text": "cases 20 minutes depending on how close",
      "start": 489.199,
      "duration": 6.161
    },
    {
      "text": "the restaurant you're ordering from is.",
      "start": 491.44,
      "duration": 3.92
    },
    {
      "text": "I recently started watching a Korean",
      "start": 507.599,
      "duration": 4.32
    },
    {
      "text": "drama called Idorai and a new episode",
      "start": 509.599,
      "duration": 4.24
    },
    {
      "text": "came out so I watched that while having",
      "start": 511.919,
      "duration": 4.92
    },
    {
      "text": "dinner.",
      "start": 513.839,
      "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
      "text": "I've been really into takoyaki lately",
      "start": 521.519,
      "duration": 3.76
    },
    {
      "text": "and I think I order it almost every",
      "start": 523.44,
      "duration": 5.16
    },
    {
      "text": "other day.",
      "start": 525.279,
      "duration": 3.321
    },
    {
      "text": "Korea is very strict about recycling. So",
      "start": 552.0,
      "duration": 3.92
    },
    {
      "text": "separating trash has become second",
      "start": 554.24,
      "duration": 4.68
    },
    {
      "text": "nature.",
      "start": 555.92,
      "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
      "text": "Now it's time for my evening routine.",
      "start": 567.44,
      "duration": 4.36
    },
    {
      "text": "One of the biggest changes since living",
      "start": 593.12,
      "duration": 3.839
    },
    {
      "text": "in Korea is how much effort I put into",
      "start": 594.8,
      "duration": 5.159
    },
    {
      "text": "skincare.",
      "start": 596.959,
      "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
      "text": "I do a sheet mask every single day.",
      "start": 608.08,
      "duration": 4.56
    },
    {
      "text": "Medill is my favorite. The fit is great",
      "start": 610.32,
      "duration": 4.0
    },
    {
      "text": "so I can move around freely while",
      "start": 612.64,
      "duration": 5.0
    },
    {
      "text": "wearing it.",
      "start": 614.32,
      "duration": 3.32
    },
    {
      "text": "Sometimes being alone feels more honest",
      "start": 629.839,
      "duration": 3.601
    },
    {
      "text": "than being surrounded by people you",
      "start": 632.0,
      "duration": 3.279
    },
    {
      "text": "don't truly connect with. And honestly,",
      "start": 633.44,
      "duration": 6.28
    },
    {
      "text": "I'm a home buddy and I like that.",
      "start": 635.279,
      "duration": 4.441
    },
    {
      "text": "Especially",
      "start": 649.04,
      "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
      "text": "for black people or like black women,",
      "start": 675.92,
      "duration": 3.76
    },
    {
      "text": "they're scared.",
      "start": 678.0,
      "duration": 4.64
    },
    {
      "text": "that I built was an AI learning app",
      "start": 679.68,
      "duration": 6.88
    },
    {
      "text": "almost a year now about a year ago.",
      "start": 682.64,
      "duration": 7.439
    },
    {
      "text": ">> After letting the mask fully absorb,",
      "start": 686.56,
      "duration": 9.0
    },
    {
      "text": "I apply an ample then essence and cream.",
      "start": 690.079,
      "duration": 5.481
    },
    {
      "text": "and finish with a spot treatment from",
      "start": 711.92,
      "duration": 3.52
    },
    {
      "text": "the pharmacy. That's the end of my",
      "start": 713.76,
      "duration": 4.48
    },
    {
      "text": "nighttime skincare routine.",
      "start": 715.44,
      "duration": 4.639
    },
    {
      "text": "I usually take out the trash late at",
      "start": 718.24,
      "duration": 4.839
    },
    {
      "text": "night,",
      "start": 720.079,
      "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
      "text": "but since I'm already outside, I will",
      "start": 725.279,
      "duration": 3.601
    },
    {
      "text": "stop by the convenience store near my",
      "start": 727.12,
      "duration": 6.36
    },
    {
      "text": "place to grab my favorite Korean drink.",
      "start": 728.88,
      "duration": 4.6
    },
    {
      "text": "It's called dichu sanati. A traditional",
      "start": 754.8,
      "duration": 5.12
    },
    {
      "text": "Korean drink you can enjoy warm. It's",
      "start": 757.76,
      "duration": 3.92
    },
    {
      "text": "especially good in winter and they say",
      "start": 759.92,
      "duration": 3.68
    },
    {
      "text": "it even helps prevent colds which I",
      "start": 761.68,
      "duration": 5.959
    },
    {
      "text": "easily catch very often.",
      "start": 763.6,
      "duration": 4.039
    },
    {
      "text": "True.",
      "start": 781.04,
      "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
      "text": "Well, thank you for watching the video.",
      "start": 797.04,
      "duration": 2.88
    },
    {
      "text": "Hope you enjoyed it. If you love to sing",
      "start": 798.32,
      "duration": 3.04
    },
    {
      "text": "more like this, be sure to let me know",
      "start": 799.92,
      "duration": 4.24
    },
    {
      "text": "in the comment section.",
      "start": 801.36,
      "duration": 2.8
    }
  ]
}